Shandong Xinhua to include in HSCEI . Medicine manufacturer Shandong Xinhua Pharmaceutical Co Ltd will be included as a constituent stock of the Hang Seng China Enterprises Index ( HSCEI ) with effect from Thursday , HSI Services Ltd said on Monday . With the addition of Shandong Xinhua , which is to be listed on the Hong Kong stock exchange on Tuesday , there will be 23 constituent stocks in the HSCEI , it said . HSCEI is to track the overall performance of all China enterprises listed in Hong Kong . The index is managed and compiled by HSI Services , a wholly - owned unit of Hang Seng Bank . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6370 
